# bevel_length_sq_sin_half show the bevel segment = 2 d sin(theta/2), the
# chord of the round-join arc (radius d, central angle = the turn).
# Three-axiom (sin_half_turn is sqrt-only).  No Admitted.
theories/BufferBevel.v
