# rational model.  xscale / xscale_edge; the forward bridge xscale_cross_bridge;
# the reverse edge_crosses_ray_xscale_rev (via xscale_inv); the mutual-induction
# parity transport ray_parity_xscale_both / ray_parity_odd_xscale; and the
# ring_edges/map commutation ring_edges_map_xscale.  Supports lifting Q-grid
# regression anchors (Spectre/hat) to the true metric.  Three-axiom.  No Admitted.
theories/HexXScaleBridge.v

