# face_outer_polygon_valid; face_polygon_holes_valid -- every valid_polygon
# condition except hole_inside_outer holds by construction of the face walks.
# No Admitted; standard three-axiom classical-reals base.
theories/FacePolygonHoles.v

# extract_rings_valid R5 analytic seam, Stage A (conditional headline): a face
# polygon with holes is valid_polygon modulo a NAMED JCT hypothesis, in geometric
